<a name=\"IMMZD2DTMeaslesMCVDose0VS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20between|206|20months|20and|209|20months-52\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageisbetween6monthsand9months-52\">Client's age is between 6 months and 9 months-52</a></td><td>Client's age is between 6 months and 9 months</td><td><div><p>6 months ≤ Today's date − \"Date of birth\" &lt; 9 months</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMeaslesMCVDose0VS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Live|20vaccine|20was|20administered|20in|20the|20last|204|20weeks-92\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Livevaccinewasadministeredinthelast4weeks-92\">Live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks-92</a></td><td>Live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date - latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Live vaccine\" = TRUE) &lt; 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMeaslesMCVDose0VS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20live|20vaccine|20was|20administered|20in|20the|20last|204|20weeks-92\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Nolivevaccinewasadministeredinthelast4weeks-92\">No live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks-92</a></td><td>No live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date - latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Live vaccine\" = TRUE) ≥ 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMeaslesMCVDose0VS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Consider|20MCV0.-90\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code>